    schema:author "China Miéville" ;
    schema:dateCreated "2005"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Looking for Jake and Other Stories" ;
    schema:review "If there is one thing that is certain when reading China Mieville's stories, it is to expect the weirdness, the differentness, and sheer creativity. This is a collection of short stories that offer glimpses of ideas. The Tain was my favourite, but others felt like snippets of novels I have already read, which made me nostalgic. I also discovered that there is a new novel coming out later this year, so good timing I suppose."@en ;
