    schema:name "Thirteen ways to kill Lulabelle Rock" ;
    schema:review "A story about hiring your clone to kill other (consensual) clones because, what?, you got bored of them? So much promise in this one, and yet it felt forced, cliched, and just not satisfying. Also felt derivated, as in to the extreme."@en ;
