    schema:dateCreated "2020"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Attack Surface" ;
    schema:review "Novelisation of American authoritarian dystopia where people use tech to degrade democracy and force people to do stuff. Based on the real world - in the sense that things are not far fetched and probably closer to what happens. Story was okay. Tech stuff was okay - a bit overexposed but still fit the story. Its depressing to read this and think that's how the world functions."@en ;
