    schema:dateCreated "2022"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Simply Maths" ;
    schema:review "I'm not sure who exactly this book is for. The illustrations seem intended for a younger audience, but the concepts themselves are far too complex to be suitable. And to further aggravate the experience, nothing is explained in either details or placed within some larger picture. The book is nothing but a fancy index of concepts, and not a good one at that. Too bad this was a gift, I had hoped to like it."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/792"^^xsd:anyURI .

