    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Iron Sunrise" ;
    schema:review "This could very well be titled 'Space Nazis fuck off'. Quite astounding how much stuff Charles Stross can fit into a book. There are characters, there is society, there is science and fiction, there are epic themes - in this case the role of technology and progress, artificial intelligence, nazis or to be more specific authoritarian religious dogma. There was even a teenager girl with a cyberspace companion. Interesting and excellent reading."@en ;
