    schema:isPartOf hplist:cork,
        hplist:scifi ;
    schema:name "Singularity Sky" ;
    schema:review "A blazing story about futurism, politics, philosophy, and impact of technological progress on society and social structures. Not only was this exciting sci-fi, but also a great read on the nature of information and its role in sociological structures like governments. Information wants to be free - a phrase that will be imprinted after reading this one."@en ;
