    schema:author "Jamie Susskind" ;
    schema:dateCreated "2022"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookNonFiction ;
    schema:isPartOf hplist:DCU ;
    schema:name "The Digital Republic: How to Govern and Take Back Control Technology" ;
    schema:review "A comprehensive book about what 'republican' means in the political context (not the American one), and how it applies to the rising digital internet economy. There's a lot of interesting concepts, and even though I knew a lot of the events and situations mentioned, the specific perspective of how they relate to things such as self-determination and governance of systems was interesting and thought-provoking."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/861"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/862> a hpcom:Book,
