    hpcom:book_status hpcom:book-read ;
    hpcom:date_book_read "2023-06-11T11:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    schema:aggregatedRating hptag:Rating3 ;
    schema:author "Glyn Moody" ;
    schema:dateCreated "2022"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookNonFiction ;
    schema:name "Walled Culture" ;
    schema:review "A short history of sorts regarding copyright and its effect on digital technology, this book was a refresher on several moments I had known but had forgotten about. Like the upload filter, Megaupload, Napster, and so on. Moments where the internet changed as I was growing up. The book didn't offer much of anything new other than these except to emphasise how the copyright movement has been affecting things for a long time and to not forget these. It would have been better to have researched some more materials and to have detailed in-depth analysis instead of a blog-style rehash of things."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/863"^^xsd:anyURI .

