    schema:name "Utopia is Creepy; and other provocations" ;
    schema:review "Interesting book that contains few thought-provoking articles, but then most of the other times its just some person rambling on a topic. Sometimes its things that don't seem sensible because I'd see biases and prejudices for a particular technology or company (mostly Apple) that taint the other writings."@en ;
