<https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/930> a hpcom:Book,
        hpcom:BookReading,
        hpcom:RenderedItem,
        schema:Book ;
    hpcom:book_id hpcom:930 ;
    hpcom:book_owned_medium hpcom:PhysicalBook ;
    hpcom:book_read_medium hpcom:PhysicalBook ;
    hpcom:book_status hpcom:book-read ;
    hpcom:date_book_read "2024-02-05T00:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime ;
    schema:aggregatedRating hptag:Rating4 ;
    schema:author "Yukio Mishima" ;
    schema:dateCreated "1962"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Beautiful Star" ;
    schema:review "I picked up the book, turned it around to read the blurb on the back cover - instant purchase! The premise is quirky and weird - four family members from different planets! The book itself is a nicely pieced together bundle of perpectives and clever observations on humanity. I could read it both ways - that these people were really aliens, or were so alienated that they prefered not to call Earth home anymore. The story does falter a bit, but it is still quite visual and interesting. The end absolutely made me sit up and pay attention to what I was reading - so theres's an extra +1 because of that. I didn't know the author was so well known - but now that I do I think about reading more."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/930"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/931> a hpcom:Book,
