    schema:name "Digital Empires: The Global Battle to Regulate Technology" ;
    schema:review "A massive tome that goes into detail regarding the emerging digital empires of USA, EU, and China and the extra-judicial effects and influences each is having - increasingly invisibly - on how technology and regulations shape up while trade gets even more complicated."@en ;
