    schema:name "Caliban's War" ;
    schema:review "Good space drama involving the same crew as the last novel, and some additional characters - just enough to show a different facet of life and politics in the expanse, and softly advancing the plot about the alien horror. If you look closely, you can even see the stereotypes and cliches and the hand wavy manner of getting out of tricky situations. Onwards to Book 3"@en ;
