    schema:name "Cibola Burn" ;
    schema:review "Book 4 continues the tale of the dramatic crew into more adventures - this time more space western than a space opera. Entertaining as a reprieve from the earlier science heavy books, hopefully this is a pit stop and we get back to more alien mysteries in the next book."@en ;
