    schema:name "Ireland's Trees: Myths, Legends and Folklore" ;
    schema:review "Lots of information about trees and how the Irish history is tangled with them. Good read, but I would have loved to read this while knowing the trees themselves in physical form. Maybe I should re-read this someday as and when I find the trees."@en ;
