    schema:dateCreated "1993"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Mindstar Rising" ;
    schema:review "Futuristic dystopian cyberpunk-ish detective thriller with some class based societal commentary. Would imagine this was creative in the decades before when it was published. Now it is interesting for the descriptions of how things work and how society gets weirder, but otherwise the actual mystery isn't quite that appealing. I bought this in the tiny pulp format -- was good to have it in the pocket."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/981"^^xsd:anyURI .

