    schema:dateCreated "2015"^^xsd:int ;
    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction,
        hpcom:BookSciFi ;
    schema:name "Nemesis Games" ;
    schema:review "Book 5: The Gang goes their separate ways and then shit happens that makes them want to get back together. I liked that this wasn't another episodic instance of the same stuff and that each character got enough of a back and individual story to have them be relevant in the larger story. I thought the pieces on Earth were a little slow and/or a little low in terms of having content. I'd have liked to see more, but that's the part where the good styorytelling comes through. Having less and wanting more is good if the overall story still is enjoying, which this was. Onwards to the next book."@en ;
    schema:url "https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/987"^^xsd:anyURI .

<https://harshp.com/hobbies/books/988> a hpcom:Book,
