    schema:name "Midnight Timetable" ;
    schema:review "A collection of ghost stories, I was initially patient that things might get more weirder, but the stories were all just meh. I understand there is an undercurrent in each that provides social commentary, but all of it felt so obviously placed, disconnected from the story itself, and also on the nose. So while interesting to read, none of the stories really stuck."@en ;
