    schema:genre hpcom:BookFiction ;
    schema:name "Living Things" ;
    schema:review "A short read about four (young) guys on a summer work program in Spain, and how their world is shaped through the experience. The writing is sharp and fluid, and keeps the story flowing. This would have been a good airport read. I didn't quite see the ending be done in a satisfying way, but that is also why the book is so short. Good writing, good storytelling."@en ;
